I found this E.P in with my other CDs [I forgot I had it] It was self-released by a band called Tube who were from where I live. They were actually pretty good when i saw them live at some small local festival so I grabbed this E.P, It&#039;s quite good and well produced. I don&#039;t know really how to describe their sound other than the rather lazy "Rock" [maybe radio friendly rock?] but basically if you like bands like "Hundred Reasons", "A", and any other of that type of british rock band you&#039;ll probably enjoy this. I cannot find anything more about the band as their website is no longer active so i assume that sadly they never made it any further or are recording under a different name. Anyway it&#039;s only a small file so if you like rock music give it a try, what have you got to lose?

Enjoy! :)
